---
title: Spicy Szechuan Veggie Noodle Stir-Fry with Scallions
description: Szechuan food is like the culinary equivalent of ziplining—its signature aromatic spices are exhilarating and may even give you an adrenaline rush. Our chefs channeled that sensation into a veggie noodle stir-fry that’s tossed in a Szechuan-style sauce. Mellowed with peanut butter and sweet soy glaze, the sauce is plentiful enough to coat springy ramen noodles and a bounty of veggies, including mushrooms, broccoli, cauliflower, and carrot. We promise the flavors will take you to new heights.
